### Statistics by category (defaults: page 0, size 20)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/statistics/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "groupBy": "CATEGORY"
}

### Statistics by IBAN
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/statistics/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "groupBy": "IBAN"
}

### Statistics by month
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/statistics/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "groupBy": "MONTH"
}

### Filter by IBAN
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/statistics/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "groupBy": "CATEGORY",
  "iban": "DE89370400440532013000"
}

### Filter by month range (May-August 2026)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/statistics/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "groupBy": "CATEGORY",
  "fromMonth": "2026-05",
  "toMonth": "2026-08"
}

### Combined: IBAN + month range + pagination
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/statistics/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "groupBy": "MONTH",
  "iban": "PL61109010140000071219812874",
  "fromMonth": "2026-01",
  "toMonth": "2026-06",
  "page": 0,
  "size": 10
}

### Pagination: page 2, size 5
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/statistics/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "groupBy": "IBAN",
  "page": 2,
  "size": 5
}
